e=Daft Punk to make appearance in 'Tron Legacy' film |url=http://www.nme.com/news/daft-punk/47693 |work= |publisher=[[NME|NME]] |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2009-10-06 |archive-date=2016-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160104182933/http://www.nme.com/news/daft-punk/47693 |dead-url=no }}</ref>推出的[[預告片|預告片]]已使用原聲帶裡的“Derezzed”曲目。<ref name=DerezzedDaftPunk>{{cite web|title=Teaser trailer with "Derezzed" by Daft Punk|date=2010-10-26|url=http://www.filmissimo.it/blog/la-colonna-sonora-di-tron-legacy-trailer-con-derezzed-dei-daft-punk.html|accessdate=2010-10-26|archive-date=2010-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101031214219/http://www.filmissimo.it/blog/la-colonna-sonora-di-tron-legacy-trailer-con-derezzed-dei-daft-punk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>電影配樂採用85人組的交響樂團，于[[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[Air_Studios|Air Studios]]錄製。<ref name="TronDisneyStudio">[http://www.waltdisneystudiosawards.com/tronlegacy/music.php Tron: Legacy | Music] {{Wayback|url=http://www.waltdisneystudiosawards.com/tronlegacy/music.php |date=20101104035555 }}. waltdisneystudiosawards.com. Retrieved November 19, 2010.</ref> 

